      <description>&lt;h1 id=&#34;welcome-to-my-personal-website&#34;&gt;Welcome to my Personal Website!&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I originally created this website using Twitter Bootstrap. However, I later decided to rebuild it with &lt;a href=&#34;https://gohugo.io/&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;Hugo&lt;/a&gt;, a platform that I had never worked with before. But to be honest, I now truly appreciate its capabilities :).&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Hugo has made it incredibly easy for me to create, manage, and publish content like what you are seeing here.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;how-i-deploy-the-site&#34;&gt;How I deploy the site?&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;















&lt;figure  &gt;
  &lt;div class=&#34;d-flex justify-content-center&#34;&gt;
    &lt;div class=&#34;w-100&#34; &gt;&lt;img alt=&#34;Deploy&#34; srcset=&#34;
               /project/website/deploy_hueca385b9fa5efe89b94401a6ef0929b9_17469_152a99f60c9f1d62206de1d7e4d6083e.webp 400w,
               /project/website/deploy_hueca385b9fa5efe89b94401a6ef0929b9_17469_87418a8b015f01ac2bcebcc1eb274df8.webp 760w,
